### Create a new class
POST http://localhost:4000/class-api/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mathematics 101",
  "department": "Mathematics",
  "faculty": "John Doe",
  "studentsCount": 30,
  "schedule": "Monday and Wednesday, 10:00 AM - 12:00 PM"
}

